An '''enzymer''' was a used to identify biological remnants and to produce a counter-agent to known [[Bacteria/Legends|bacteria]] and viruses. [[Callista Ming]] acquired a [[BioTech Industries/Legends|BioTech Industries]] [[Mark 16 Enzymer]] from the [[Bith/Legends|Bith]] known as [[Numbers (Bith)|Numbers]] while on [[Gamorr/Legends|Gamorr]] and used it to discover that a [[kheilwar]] had killed a local [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorrean]].

